on the train, or leave their top secret laptops open at the coffee shop whi=
le they go to the bathroom, or have loud top secret phone conversations in =
public places, or are actual spies for the other side. At 1.2 million peopl=
e, no matter how good your vetting is, the far left tail of the trustworthi=
